---
title: Smoked Haddock, Cod and Salmon Puff Pastry Pie with Dill and Garlicky Green Beans
description: A comfort food classic using premium ingredients, this Smoked Haddock, Cod and Salmon Puff Pastry Pie brings the best of the British pub into your kitchen.

Say hello to a fresh ingredient - fish pie mix! Delicious in fish pies but also all kinds of seafood dishes, this versatile mix contains flavoursome haddock, delicate cod and flaky salmon.
